race.comment: Competitive. LECAN (10) has been threatening another win for the Freedman yard. He will use the inside barrier and steps up from a mile. Should be back in the finish. PROCLAIMER (7) finished ahead of the above here last time, and it was a big effort after settling last. Turned the form around and will jump shorter today. SEACRYPTION (12) has been racing well without winning. She gets another chance in this contest. SUPER FAIR (4) has a wide gate but she comes back in trip and plenty in grade. On an 8-day return and can't be ruled out. WHATJEUDOIN' (8) has been knocking on the door including a last start second over 2000m at Warwick when only a nose from the winner. In the mix.
